Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========TEXT==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直都被研美騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果相信他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們遲早也會跟他走上同一條路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.00,0:00:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次才終於感覺到自己的認知是多麼的膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須繃緊神經才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽同學 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 發生了太多的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有留下什麼可怕的回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我相信阿爾瑪同學一定會來救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之嗎


Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是研美集團過去十年的企業報告

Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:36.88,OT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,500)\fs25\pos(77,117)}#08\N 傾注真心

Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只調查到這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只是些形式上的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來進行單獨調查比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用自己的管道試試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不儘快找出深藏的敵人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽 出發吧鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所指示的物品也已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少由我來說明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 因為這是我自己決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~啊 都濕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為社團活動時間太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 藍羽同學他們請假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微...等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.23,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼煞風景的房間啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是契約
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之前一直都沒有理會阿爾瑪同學的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是將我自己單方面的認知強加於阿爾瑪同學身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學自己是不得已才被捲進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.52,0:04:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後和我訂下契約 大家相互幫忙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼 意思是說我死了之後能得到一大筆錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先放在我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你以「總之就這樣吧」的心情戰鬥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就這麼讓妳信不過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂契約什麼的果然太不通情理了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要維持和阿爾瑪同學的關係 就只有這個方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是瑠璃抱著請求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分男人都會被秒殺的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能做那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要阿爾瑪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人不得安寧的傢伙啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法了…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是為了什麼而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你以「總之就這樣吧」的心情戰鬥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的需要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼瓦它…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點就掛了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要修理啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望兩位幫我找到作為修復材料的石頭啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的石頭是不行的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也不行啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是「傾注真心」的石頭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那如同玻璃般脆弱的心將會一分為二的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是一團黏土…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 為什麼我得這麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只剩3天可活了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓瑠璃一個人去我的出生地鐮倉怎麼能讓人放心的下啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我一個人去沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在鐮倉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 「傾注真心」的石頭是什麼樣的石頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是 男女之間恩恩愛愛產出的結晶啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我說的太高深了嗎啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到那種石頭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位必須手牽手才行啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不對勁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 只是很少見到妳這麼穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女僕們幫我想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪怪的…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳第一次坐有軌電車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我一直都是坐專車的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把你牽扯進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 本來也是我自己說要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到那種石頭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位必須手牽手才行啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車馬上就要進入三號線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:34.77,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了您的安全 請站在黃線外候車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要一起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你正忙的時候打擾真是過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自哈佛畢業之後就再也沒見過面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你會當官之類的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有更重要的使命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的話應該能成為國之棟樑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太抬舉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這個…拜託你的那件事如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要對研美集團出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會被抹殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我一句 別再插手這件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是江之電嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.91,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江の電 起點是藤澤市終點是鐮倉市的電車 全名江之島電鐵線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.44,0:11:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為妳又被拐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 是我只顧著東張西望了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦 總之沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係了啦 我不會再左顧右盼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大佛是在那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:11:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本大佛殿好像就是在這的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…這個就是鬼瓦的兄弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遲啊瑠璃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 很恩愛的親嘴嘴了嗎啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別喊那麼大聲 對裂縫會有影響的啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經得到碎片了 這樣就可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有發光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人傾注真心的話石頭應該會發光的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手有好好牽在一起嗎啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼瓦怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它說石頭在發光之前 手要一直牽著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…先去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿爾瑪同學一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳來真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 特大碗金槍魚叉燒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.60,0:13:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不一起來還比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼一直這副表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 有什麼話妳就說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不說我怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生什麼的氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於昨天訂契約的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一起來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很討厭嗎 和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是討厭就不會一起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和惡石戰鬥的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問都不用問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之什麼的 阿爾瑪同學每一次每一次都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的總之不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是很不情願的萬般無奈的戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很認真的想著要救人要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎 是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直讓她感到不安嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種細微的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.84,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想在這種店裡吃一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是因為我沒好好的傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點又要被我破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙您款待了 真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我吃過的拉麵裡最好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你告訴我啊 我也一樣 不和我說我怎麼會知道的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是朋友…的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒發光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時就這樣觀察一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 難得來這裡 要一起走走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那個矮小的阿爾瑪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在長的還真高大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候在鐮倉住的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我讀小學之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我剛懂事的時候 老爸就已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽同學應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學的資料 全都在鏡手上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多 阿爾瑪同學的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬過來之後 馬上就交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然互相都不知道名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天過的都很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是囂張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無法原諒 而使用了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都因為這種原因搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是…失去朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直起脊梁好好振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你自己能好好振作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會破壞你和重要的人之間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…從那時起一點也沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡對阿爾瑪來說是重要的地方吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 帶著妳到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果到最後石頭也沒發光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那個時候有見到過阿爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在建設中的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這麼多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直禁止游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為橫須賀那邊好像發生了什麼事故
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在總算開放了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都捨不得離開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿爾瑪同學守護住了大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 得救的人還有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼涼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾瑪同學不來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝殼還是什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是別人給的賣剩貨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常正好相反呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我先收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是總之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.40,0:20:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我接受妳的「意志」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我一個人什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果和妳在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才明白了破壞的力量也能用來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 瑠璃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼啊 當然是那個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行到哪步了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…到江之島了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是阿爾瑪的這個喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 真吵啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼修好了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為修理了啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心的石頭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過愛的結晶 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火熱火熱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受鐮倉的約會了嗎鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙騙了我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次雖然沒有得到決定性的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.57,0:22:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於研美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要深加調查
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍羽財團攪和進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.95,0:22:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被奈特的話所擺佈了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙會查出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時候…

