Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:36.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}比任何謊言都要過分的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:38.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}you are my devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.53,0:23:42.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}已經再也無法逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:44.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}那是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:49.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}還是僅僅為了我而緊繫的passion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:52.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}哪怕就算相愛 也總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:55.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,266)}終會落得形單影隻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:59.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}被一次微笑所拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:02.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}那微小柔弱的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:05.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,266)}不斷努力 不斷跌倒
